OL,5, An urgent review of rights available to
OL,6, victims after their court cases are    
OL,7, dropped has been urged by Labour.      
OL,9,FIt comes after the CPS apologised to a 
OL,10,Fwoman whose rape case was wrongfully   
OL,11,Fclosed over claims she had an episode  
OL,12,Fof sexsomnia, a rare sleep condition.  
OL,14,FThe BBC found 60 cases in 2021/22 which
OL,15,Fthe CPS admitted wrongly dropping, but 
OL,16,Fthe cases can no longer be pursued.    
OL,18,FThe CPS said decisions to halt cases   
OL,19,Fwere never taken lightly.              
